data.name: Label1.Text
data.value:
To use the remote features , you must have a Dropbox or any file hosting account. Create a textfile in Dropbox , in the file write "false" without quotes. Save the file, then copy the direct file link and paste it into the textbox above. The program will check the file if any of the following conditions are met.
If the file reads "false" , nothing will happen. If it reads "true" then the requested operation will be performed.

data.name: Label4.Text
data.value: When you change the value of the text file, make sure you change it back to its original state to prevent multiple requests. For example, change true back to false.
